WITH cardiac_output_patients AS (
 SELECT DISTINCT hadm_id
 FROM procedures_icd
 WHERE icd_code = (SELECT icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE long_title = 'performance of cardiac output, continuous')
 AND strftime('%Y', charttime) = '2100'
),
frequent_tests AS (
 SELECT test_name, COUNT(*) AS frequency
 FROM microbiologyevents
 WHERE hadm_id IN (SELECT hadm_id FROM cardiac_output_patients)
 AND strftime('%Y', charttime) = '2100'
 GROUP BY test_name
 ORDER BY frequency DESC
 LIMIT 3
)

FROM frequent_tests;

WITH procedure_admissions AS (
 SELECT hadm_id
 FROM procedures_icd
 JOIN d_icd_procedures ON procedures_icd.icd_code = d_icd_procedures.icd_code
 WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'cardiac output, continuous procedure'
),
current_year_tests AS (

 WHERE hadm_id IN (SELECT hadm_id FROM procedure_admissions)
 AND strftime('%Y', charttime) = '2100'
 GROUP BY test_name
),
ranked_tests AS (
 SELECT test_name, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY test_count DESC) AS rank

)

SELECT D.long_title 
FROM procedures_icd AS P 
JOIN admissions AS A ON P.hadm_id = A.hadm_id 
JOIN patients AS PT ON A.subject_id = PT.subject_id 
JOIN d_icd_procedures AS D ON P.icd_code = D.icd_code 
WHERE (2100 - CAST(strftime('%Y', PT.dob) AS INTEGER)) BETWEEN 20 AND 29 
AND strftime('%Y', P.charttime) = '2100' 
GROUP BY P.icd_code 
ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC 
LIMIT 3;

WITH PatientAge AS (
 SELECT p.subject_id, 
 (2100 - CAST(strftime('%Y', p.dob) AS INTEGER)) AS age
 FROM patients p
),
ProceduresCount AS (
 SELECT dp.long_title, COUNT(*) AS freq
 FROM PatientAge pa
 JOIN admissions a ON pa.subject_id = a.subject_id
 JOIN procedures_icd pi ON a.hadm_id = pi.hadm_id
 JOIN d_icd_procedures dp ON pi.icd_code = dp.icd_code
 WHERE pa.age BETWEEN 20 AND 29
 GROUP BY dp.long_title
),
RankedProcedures AS (
 SELECT long_title, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY freq DESC) AS rank
 FROM ProceduresCount
)
SELECT long_title
FROM RankedProcedures
WHERE rank <= 3;

WITH first_diagnosis AS (
 SELECT di.subject_id, MIN(di.charttime) AS first_charttime
 FROM diagnoses_icd di
 JOIN d_icd_diagnoses dd ON di.icd_code = dd.icd_code
 WHERE dd.long_title = 'Nontoxic multinodular goiter'
 GROUP BY di.subject_id
),

survival_status AS (
 SELECT fd.subject_id,
 CASE WHEN p.dod IS NULL OR p.dod > datetime(fd.first_charttime, '+182 days') THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS survived
 FROM first_diagnosis fd
 LEFT JOIN patients p ON fd.subject_id = p.subject_id
)

SELECT AVG(survived) AS six_month_survival_rate
FROM survival_status;
8bbf2b3bc2d3b533c39eaeb5:
WITH diagnosed_patients AS (
 SELECT di.subject_id, MIN(di.charttime) AS first_diagnosis_time
 FROM diagnoses_icd di
 JOIN d_icd_diagnoses dicd ON di.icd_code = dicd.icd_code
 WHERE dicd.long_title = 'Nontoxic multinodular goiter'
 GROUP BY di.subject_id
),
patient_survival AS (
 SELECT dp.subject_id,
 CASE WHEN p.dod IS NULL OR p.dod > datetime(dp.first_diagnosis_time, '+182.5 days') THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS survived
 FROM diagnosed_patients dp
 LEFT JOIN patients p ON dp.subject_id = p.subject_id
)

FROM patient_survival;

WITH goiter_patients AS (
 SELECT DISTINCT d.subject_id, a.admittime
 FROM diagnoses_icd d
 JOIN d_icd_diagnoses di ON d.icd_code = di.icd_code
 JOIN admissions a ON d.hadm_id = a.hadm_id
 WHERE di.long_title = 'Nontoxic multinodular goiter'
),
survived_patients AS (
 SELECT gp.subject_id
 FROM goiter_patients gp
 LEFT JOIN patients p ON gp.subject_id = p.subject_id
 WHERE p.dod IS NULL OR p.dod > datetime(gp.admittime, '+6 months')
)
SELECT CAST(COUNT(sp.subject_id) AS FLOAT) / COUNT(gp.subject_id) AS survival_proportion
FROM goiter_patients gp
LEFT JOIN survived_patients sp ON gp.subject_id = sp.subject_id;

WITH mycoses_diagnoses AS (
 SELECT di.subject_id, di.hadm_id, di.charttime
 FROM diagnoses_icd di
 JOIN d_icd_diagnoses dicd ON di.icd_code = dicd.icd_code
 WHERE dicd.long_title = 'other and unspecified mycoses'
),
subsequent_diagnoses AS (
 SELECT di.subject_id, di.icd_code, dicd.long_title, COUNT(*) AS freq
 FROM diagnoses_icd di
 JOIN mycoses_diagnoses md ON di.subject_id = md.subject_id AND di.hadm_id = md.hadm_id
 JOIN d_icd_diagnoses dicd ON di.icd_code = dicd.icd_code
 WHERE di.charttime > md.charttime AND di.charttime <= datetime(md.charttime, '+2 months')
 GROUP BY di.subject_id, di.icd_code
),
ranked_diagnoses AS (
 SELECT long_title, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY SUM(freq) DESC) AS rank
 FROM subsequent_diagnoses
 GROUP BY long_title
)
SELECT long_title
FROM ranked_diagnoses
WHERE rank <= 3;
7c33e8ff9f7c09e92c203ef0:
WITH mycoses_diagnoses AS (
 SELECT di.subject_id, di.hadm_id, di.charttime
 FROM diagnoses_icd di
 JOIN d_icd_diagnoses dicd ON di.icd_code = dicd.icd_code
 WHERE dicd.long_title = 'other and unspecified mycoses'
),
subsequent_diagnoses AS (
 SELECT di2.icd_code, COUNT(*) AS freq
 FROM mycoses_diagnoses md
 JOIN diagnoses_icd di2 ON md.subject_id = di2.subject_id AND di2.charttime > md.charttime AND di2.charttime <= datetime(md.charttime, '+60 days')
 WHERE md.hadm_id != di2.hadm_id
 GROUP BY di2.icd_code
)
SELECT dicd.long_title
FROM subsequent_diagnoses sd
JOIN d_icd_diagnoses dicd ON sd.icd_code = dicd.icd_code
ORDER BY sd.freq DESC
LIMIT 3;

WITH initial_diagnoses AS (
 SELECT di.subject_id, di.hadm_id, di.charttime AS initial_charttime
 FROM diagnoses_icd di
 JOIN d_icd_diagnoses dicd ON di.icd_code = dicd.icd_code
 WHERE dicd.long_title = 'other and unspecified mycoses'
),
subsequent_diagnoses AS (
 SELECT sd.icd_code, COUNT(*) AS count
 FROM initial_diagnoses id
 JOIN diagnoses_icd sd ON id.subject_id = sd.subject_id
 WHERE sd.charttime > id.initial_charttime
 AND sd.charttime <= datetime(id.initial_charttime, '+2 months')
 GROUP BY sd.icd_code
),
ranked_diagnoses AS (
 SELECT sd.icd_code, sd.count, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY sd.count DESC) AS rank
 FROM subsequent_diagnoses sd
)
SELECT dicd.long_title

 FROM prescriptions P1
 JOIN prescriptions P2 ON P1.subject_id = P2.subject_id AND P1.hadm_id = P2.hadm_id
 WHERE P1.drug = 'gemfibrozil'
 AND datetime(P1.starttime) >= datetime('2100-12-31 23:59:00', '-1 year')
 AND P2.drug != 'gemfibrozil'
 AND datetime(P2.starttime) >= datetime('2100-12-31 23:59:00', '-1 year')
 AND datetime(P2.starttime) <= datetime(P1.stoptime)
 GROUP BY P2.drug
 ORDER BY frequency DESC
 LIMIT 5
) AS top_concurrent_drugs;

WITH FirstDiagnosis AS (
 SELECT di.subject_id, di.icd_code, MIN(di.charttime) AS first_diagnosis_time
 FROM diagnoses_icd di
 GROUP BY di.subject_id, di.icd_code
),
Mortality AS (
 SELECT fd.icd_code, COUNT(CASE WHEN julianday(p.dod) - julianday(fd.first_diagnosis_time) <= 182.5 THEN 1 END) AS deaths_within_6_months,
 COUNT(*) AS total_patients
 FROM FirstDiagnosis fd
 JOIN patients p ON fd.subject_id = p.subject_id
 WHERE p.dod IS NOT NULL
 GROUP BY fd.icd_code
),
MortalityRate AS (
 SELECT m.icd_code, (1.0 * m.deaths_within_6_months / m.total_patients) AS mortality_rate
 FROM Mortality m
)
SELECT d.long_title
FROM MortalityRate mr
JOIN d_icd_diagnoses d ON mr.icd_code = d.icd_code
ORDER BY mr.mortality_rate DESC
LIMIT 4;

WITH mortality AS (
 SELECT 
 d.icd_code, 
 COUNT(CASE WHEN p.dod IS NOT NULL AND p.dod <= datetime(a.admittime, '+182.5 days') THEN 1 END) AS deaths,
 COUNT(*) AS total_admissions
 FROM diagnoses_icd d
 JOIN admissions a ON d.hadm_id = a.hadm_id
 JOIN patients p ON a.subject_id = p.subject_id
 GROUP BY d.icd_code
),
rate AS (
 SELECT 
 icd_code, 
 (1.0 * deaths / total_admissions) AS mortality_rate
 FROM mortality
),
ranked_diagnoses AS (
 SELECT 
 r.icd_code, 
 d.long_title, 
 r.mortality_rate,
 DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY r.mortality_rate DESC) AS rank
 FROM rate r
 JOIN d_icd_diagnoses d ON r.icd_code = d.icd_code
)
SELECT long_title
FROM ranked_diagnoses
WHERE rank <= 4;

WITH MortalityRates AS (
 SELECT 
 d.icd_code, 
 COUNT(DISTINCT a.hadm_id) AS total_admissions,
 SUM(CASE WHEN p.dod IS NOT NULL AND p.dod <= DATETIME(a.admittime, '+182.5 days') THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS deaths
 FROM diagnoses_icd d
 JOIN admissions a ON d.hadm_id = a.hadm_id
 JOIN patients p ON a.subject_id = p.subject_id
 GROUP BY d.icd_code
),
RankedDiagnoses AS (
 SELECT 
 m.icd_code,
 (CAST(m.deaths AS FLOAT) / m.total_admissions) AS mortality_rate,
 DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY (CAST(m.deaths AS FLOAT) / m.total_admissions) DESC) AS rank
 FROM MortalityRates m
)
SELECT d.long_title
FROM RankedDiagnoses r
JOIN d_icd_diagnoses d ON r.icd_code = d.icd_code
WHERE r.rank <= 4;

WITH cerebral_edema_diagnoses AS (
 SELECT di.subject_id, di.hadm_id, di.charttime
 FROM diagnoses_icd di
 JOIN d_icd_diagnoses dicd ON di.icd_code = dicd.icd_code
 WHERE dicd.long_title = 'Cerebral edema' AND
 datetime(di.charttime) >= datetime('2100-12-31 23:59:00', '-1 year')
),
filtered_patients AS (
 SELECT p.subject_id, a.hadm_id
 FROM patients p
 JOIN admissions a ON p.subject_id = a.subject_id
 WHERE p.gender = 'f' AND
 (strftime('%Y', '2100-12-31') - strftime('%Y', p.dob)) - 
 (strftime('%m-%d', '2100-12-31') < strftime('%m-%d', p.dob)) >= 60
),
relevant_prescriptions AS (
 SELECT pr.drug
 FROM prescriptions pr
 JOIN cerebral_edema_diagnoses ced ON pr.subject_id = ced.subject_id AND pr.hadm_id = ced.hadm_id
 JOIN filtered_patients fp ON pr.subject_id = fp.subject_id AND pr.hadm_id = fp.hadm_id
 WHERE datetime(pr.starttime, 'start of month') = datetime(ced.charttime, 'start of month')
)
SELECT drug
FROM (
 SELECT drug, COUNT(*) as freq,
 DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC) as rnk
 FROM relevant_prescriptions
 GROUP BY drug
) ranked_drugs
WHERE rnk <= 4;
dc5e1524d4fa179964024b9c:
SELECT drug FROM (
 SELECT P.drug, COUNT(*) as freq
 FROM prescriptions P
 JOIN admissions A ON P.subject_id = A.subject_id AND P.hadm_id = A.hadm_id
 JOIN patients PT ON A.subject_id = PT.subject_id
 JOIN diagnoses_icd D ON A.hadm_id = D.hadm_id
 JOIN d_icd_diagnoses DI ON D.icd_code = DI.icd_code
 WHERE PT.gender = 'f'
 AND (strftime('%Y', '2100-12-31') - strftime('%Y', PT.dob)) >= 60
 AND datetime(A.admittime) >= datetime('2100-12-31 23:59:00','-1 year')
 AND DI.long_title LIKE '%cerebral edema%'
 AND datetime(P.starttime, 'start of month') = datetime(D.charttime, 'start of month')
 GROUP BY P.drug
 ORDER BY freq DESC
 LIMIT 4
) AS TopDrugs;

FROM (
 SELECT DISTINCT C.hadm_id, SUM(C.cost) AS total_cost
 FROM diagnoses_icd AS D
 JOIN d_icd_diagnoses AS DI ON D.icd_code = DI.icd_code
 JOIN cost AS C ON D.hadm_id = C.hadm_id
 WHERE DI.long_title LIKE '%cerebral edema%'
 AND datetime(C.chargetime, 'start of year') = datetime('2100-12-31 23:59:00', 'start of year', '-0 year')
 GROUP BY C.hadm_id
) AS subquery;

SELECT AVG(C.total_cost) AS average_cost
FROM (
 SELECT A.hadm_id, SUM(COST.cost) AS total_cost
 FROM admissions AS A
 JOIN diagnoses_icd AS D ON A.hadm_id = D.hadm_id
 JOIN cost AS COST ON A.hadm_id = COST.hadm_id

 WHERE ICD.long_title LIKE '%cerebral edema%'
 AND COST.event_type = 'diagnoses_icd'

 GROUP BY A.hadm_id
) AS C;

WITH FirstProcedure AS (
 SELECT DISTINCT subject_id, hadm_id, charttime
 FROM procedures_icd
 WHERE icd_code = (SELECT icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE long_title = 'irrigation of genitourinary tract using irrigating substance, via natural or artificial opening')
 AND datetime(charttime) >= datetime('2100-12-31 23:59:00', '-1 year')
),
SecondProcedure AS (
 SELECT DISTINCT subject_id, hadm_id, charttime
 FROM procedures_icd
 WHERE icd_code = (SELECT icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE long_title = 'dilation of coronary artery, one artery with drug-eluting intraluminal device, percutaneous approach')
)
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT F.subject_id) AS patient_count
FROM FirstProcedure F
JOIN SecondProcedure S ON F.subject_id = S.subject_id AND F.hadm_id = S.hadm_id
WHERE datetime(F.charttime, 'start of month') = datetime(S.charttime, 'start of month');

WITH procedure_codes AS (
 SELECT icd_code
 FROM d_icd_procedures
 WHERE long_title = 'dilation of coronary artery, one artery with drug-eluting intraluminal device, percutaneous approach'
 OR long_title = 'irrigation of genitourinary tract using irrigating substance, via natural or artificial opening'
),
coronary_procedures AS (
 SELECT subject_id, hadm_id, charttime
 FROM procedures_icd
 WHERE icd_code = (SELECT icd_code FROM procedure_codes WHERE long_title = 'dilation of coronary artery, one artery with drug-eluting intraluminal device, percutaneous approach')
),
genitourinary_procedures AS (
 SELECT subject_id, hadm_id, charttime
 FROM procedures_icd
 WHERE icd_code = (SELECT icd_code FROM procedure_codes WHERE long_title = 'irrigation of genitourinary tract using irrigating substance, via natural or artificial opening')
)
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT coronary_procedures.subject_id) AS patient_count
FROM coronary_procedures
JOIN genitourinary_procedures
ON coronary_procedures.subject_id = genitourinary_procedures.subject_id
AND coronary_procedures.hadm_id = genitourinary_procedures.hadm_id
AND datetime(coronary_procedures.charttime, 'start of month') = datetime(genitourinary_procedures.charttime, 'start of month')
AND datetime(coronary_procedures.charttime) > datetime(genitourinary_procedures.charttime)
WHERE datetime(coronary_procedures.charttime) >= datetime('2100-12-31 23:59:00', '-1 year')
ba6f7e69053be2c46e5eb74c:
WITH ProcedureCodes AS (
 SELECT icd_code AS dilation_code
 FROM d_icd_procedures
 WHERE long_title = 'dilation of coronary artery, one artery with drug-eluting intraluminal device, percutaneous approach'
),
IrrigationCodes AS (
 SELECT icd_code AS irrigation_code
 FROM d_icd_procedures
 WHERE long_title = 'irrigation of genitourinary tract using irrigating substance, via natural or artificial opening'
),
IrrigationPatients AS (
 SELECT DISTINCT subject_id, hadm_id, charttime
 FROM procedures_icd
 WHERE icd_code IN (SELECT irrigation_code FROM IrrigationCodes)
 AND datetime(charttime) >= datetime('2100-12-31 23:59:00', '-1 year')
),
DilationPatients AS (
 SELECT DISTINCT subject_id, hadm_id, charttime
 FROM procedures_icd
 WHERE icd_code IN (SELECT dilation_code FROM ProcedureCodes)
 AND datetime(charttime) >= datetime('2100-12-31 23:59:00', '-1 year')
)
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT I.subject_id) AS patient_count
FROM IrrigationPatients I
JOIN DilationPatients D ON I.subject_id = D.subject_id AND I.hadm_id = D.hadm_id
WHERE datetime(I.charttime, 'start of month') = datetime(D.charttime, 'start of month')
AND I.charttime < D.charttime;

WITH cholangitis_patients AS (
 SELECT DISTINCT d.subject_id, a.admittime
 FROM diagnoses_icd d
 JOIN admissions a ON d.hadm_id = a.hadm_id
 WHERE d.icd_code IN (SELECT icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE long_title LIKE '%cholangitis%')
),

sodium_chloride_patients AS (
 SELECT DISTINCT p.subject_id, p.starttime
 FROM prescriptions p
 WHERE p.drug LIKE '%iso-osmotic sodium chloride%'
),

eligible_patients AS (
 SELECT c.subject_id, c.admittime
 FROM cholangitis_patients c
 JOIN sodium_chloride_patients s ON c.subject_id = s.subject_id
 WHERE s.starttime >= c.admittime AND s.starttime < c.admittime + INTERVAL '91 days'
),

survival_status AS (
 SELECT e.subject_id,
 CASE WHEN p.dod IS NULL OR p.dod > e.admittime + INTERVAL '91 days' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS survived
 FROM eligible_patients e
 LEFT JOIN patients p ON e.subject_id = p.subject_id
)

SELECT AVG(survived) AS survival_rate
FROM survival_status;

WITH CholangitisPatients AS (
 SELECT di.subject_id, di.hadm_id, di.charttime AS diagnosis_time
 FROM diagnoses_icd di
 JOIN d_icd_diagnoses dicd ON di.icd_code = dicd.icd_code
 WHERE dicd.long_title LIKE '%cholangitis%'
),
PrescribedPatients AS (
 SELECT p.subject_id, p.hadm_id, p.starttime AS prescription_time
 FROM prescriptions p
 WHERE p.drug = 'iso-osmotic sodium chloride'
),
EligiblePatients AS (
 SELECT cp.subject_id, cp.diagnosis_time
 FROM CholangitisPatients cp
 JOIN PrescribedPatients pp ON cp.subject_id = pp.subject_id AND cp.hadm_id = pp.hadm_id
 WHERE pp.prescription_time > cp.diagnosis_time
),
SurvivalStatus AS (
 SELECT ep.subject_id,
 CASE WHEN pt.dod IS NULL OR pt.dod > datetime(ep.diagnosis_time, '+91 days') THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS survived
 FROM EligiblePatients ep
 LEFT JOIN patients pt ON ep.subject_id = pt.subject_id
)
SELECT AVG(survived) AS survival_rate
FROM SurvivalStatus;

 FROM diagnoses_icd d
 JOIN d_icd_diagnoses dicd ON d.icd_code = dicd.icd_code
 WHERE dicd.long_title LIKE '%cholangitis%'
 GROUP BY d.subject_id, d.hadm_id
),

prescribed_patients AS (
 SELECT DISTINCT p.subject_id, p.hadm_id
 FROM prescriptions p
 WHERE p.drug LIKE '%iso-osmotic sodium chloride%'
),

eligible_patients AS (
 SELECT c.subject_id, c.first_diagnosis_time
 FROM cholangitis_patients c
 JOIN prescribed_patients p ON c.subject_id = p.subject_id AND c.hadm_id = p.hadm_id
),

survival_data AS (
 SELECT e.subject_id,
 CASE WHEN (julianday(patients.dod) - julianday(e.first_diagnosis_time)) > 91 OR patients.dod IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS survived
 FROM eligible_patients e
 LEFT JOIN patients ON e.subject_id = patients.subject_id
)

SELECT AVG(survived) AS three_month_survival_rate
FROM survival_data;

WITH patient_diagnosis AS (
 SELECT di.subject_id, di.hadm_id, di.charttime AS diagnosis_time
 FROM diagnoses_icd di
 JOIN d_icd_diagnoses dicd ON di.icd_code = dicd.icd_code
 WHERE dicd.long_title = 'subendocardial infarction, initial episode of care'
),
patient_age AS (
 SELECT a.subject_id, a.hadm_id, a.admittime,
 (strftime('%Y', a.admittime) - strftime('%Y', p.dob)) - 
 (strftime('%m-%d', a.admittime) < strftime('%m-%d', p.dob)) AS age
 FROM admissions a
 JOIN patients p ON a.subject_id = p.subject_id
),
relevant_patients AS (
 SELECT pd.subject_id, pd.hadm_id, pd.diagnosis_time
 FROM patient_diagnosis pd
 JOIN patient_age pa ON pd.subject_id = pa.subject_id AND pd.hadm_id = pa.hadm_id
 WHERE pa.age BETWEEN 50 AND 59
),
prescriptions_within_2_months AS (
 SELECT pr.drug
 FROM prescriptions pr
 JOIN relevant_patients rp ON pr.subject_id = rp.subject_id AND pr.hadm_id = rp.hadm_id
 WHERE datetime(pr.starttime) BETWEEN rp.diagnosis_time AND datetime(rp.diagnosis_time, '+2 months')
)
SELECT drug
FROM (
 SELECT drug, COUNT(*) AS count
 FROM prescriptions_within_2_months
 GROUP BY drug
 ORDER BY count DESC
 LIMIT 5
)

WITH recent_diagnoses AS (
 SELECT di.subject_id, di.hadm_id, di.charttime
 FROM diagnoses_icd di
 JOIN d_icd_diagnoses dicd ON di.icd_code = dicd.icd_code
 WHERE dicd.long_title LIKE '%long term (current) use of antithrombotics/antiplatelets%'
 AND datetime(di.charttime) >= datetime('2100-12-31 23:59:00', '-1 year')
),
lab_tests AS (
 SELECT le.itemid, COUNT(*) as frequency
 FROM recent_diagnoses rd
 JOIN labevents le ON rd.subject_id = le.subject_id AND rd.hadm_id = le.hadm_id
 WHERE datetime(le.charttime, 'start of month') = datetime(rd.charttime, 'start of month')
 GROUP BY le.itemid
)
SELECT dli.label
FROM lab_tests lt
JOIN d_labitems dli ON lt.itemid = dli.itemid
ORDER BY lt.frequency DESC
LIMIT 4;
6a2ce899fba50897d40de57b:
WITH current_antithrombotics AS (
 SELECT DISTINCT subject_id, hadm_id, starttime
 FROM prescriptions
 WHERE drug LIKE '%antithrombotic%' OR drug LIKE '%antiplatelet%'
 AND stoptime IS NULL
),
recent_labevents AS (
 SELECT le.subject_id, le.hadm_id, le.itemid
 FROM labevents le
 JOIN current_antithrombotics ca ON le.subject_id = ca.subject_id AND le.hadm_id = ca.hadm_id
 WHERE datetime(le.charttime) >= datetime('2100-12-31 23:59:00', '-1 year')
 AND datetime(le.charttime, 'start of month') = datetime(ca.starttime, 'start of month')
),
ranked_labs AS (
 SELECT le.itemid, COUNT(*) AS frequency,
 DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC) AS rank
 FROM recent_labevents le
 GROUP BY le.itemid
)
SELECT d.label
FROM ranked_labs rl
JOIN d_labitems d ON rl.itemid = d.itemid
WHERE rl.rank <= 4;

WHERE rt.rank <= 4;

WITH FirstAdmission AS (
 SELECT hadm_id
 FROM admissions
 WHERE subject_id = 10004235
 ORDER BY admittime ASC
 LIMIT 1
),
AnionGapMeasurements AS (
 SELECT valuenum
 FROM labevents
 WHERE subject_id = 10004235
 AND hadm_id = (SELECT hadm_id FROM FirstAdmission)
 AND itemid = (SELECT itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE label = 'anion gap')
 ORDER BY charttime ASC
 LIMIT 2
)
SELECT CASE
 WHEN COUNT(*) = 2 AND MIN(valuenum) < MAX(valuenum) THEN 'Yes'
 ELSE 'No'
END AS is_second_less_than_first
FROM AnionGapMeasurements;
ea120da1a8374c7abb430916:
WITH AnionGapMeasurements AS (
 SELECT le.valuenum AS anion_gap, le.charttime
 FROM labevents le
 JOIN d_labitems di ON le.itemid = di.itemid
 JOIN admissions ad ON le.hadm_id = ad.hadm_id
 WHERE le.subject_id = 10004235
 AND di.label = 'anion gap'
 AND ad.subject_id = 10004235
 ORDER BY ad.admittime ASC, le.charttime ASC
 LIMIT 2
)
SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 2 AND MIN(anion_gap) > MAX(anion_gap) THEN 'Yes' ELSE 'No' END AS is_second_less
FROM AnionGapMeasurements;
43e06bdf6f889def5640a6aa:
WITH AnionGapValues AS (
 SELECT le.valuenum AS anion_gap_value, le.charttime
 FROM admissions AS a
 JOIN labevents AS le ON a.hadm_id = le.hadm_id
 JOIN d_labitems AS dli ON le.itemid = dli.itemid
 WHERE a.subject_id = 10004235
 AND dli.label = 'anion gap'
 ORDER BY a.admittime ASC, le.charttime ASC
 LIMIT 2
)
SELECT CASE
 WHEN MIN(anion_gap_value) < MAX(anion_gap_value) THEN 'Yes'
 ELSE 'No'
END AS result
FROM AnionGapValues;

WITH current_visit AS (
 SELECT hadm_id
 FROM admissions
 WHERE subject_id = 10018081 AND dischtime IS NULL
),
last_emergency_transfer AS (
 SELECT intime
 FROM transfers
 WHERE subject_id = 10018081 AND careunit = 'emergency' AND hadm_id = (SELECT hadm_id FROM current_visit)
 ORDER BY intime DESC
 LIMIT 1
)
SELECT (julianday('2100-12-31 23:59:00') - julianday(intime)) * 24 AS hours_elapsed
FROM last_emergency_transfer;

SELECT ROUND((JULIANDAY('2100-12-31 23:59:00') - JULIANDAY(T2.outtime)) * 24) AS hours_since_last_emergency_stay
FROM admissions AS T1
JOIN transfers AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id
WHERE T1.subject_id = 10018081
AND T1.dischtime IS NULL
AND T2.careunit = 'emergency department'
AND T2.outtime = (
 SELECT MAX(outtime)
 FROM transfers
 WHERE subject_id = 10018081
 AND careunit = 'emergency department'
 AND hadm_id = T1.hadm_id
);

WITH AgeFilteredPatients AS (
 SELECT p.subject_id
 FROM patients p
 WHERE STRFTIME('%Y', '2100-12-31') - STRFTIME('%Y', p.dob) >= 60
),
DiagnosisFrequency AS (
 SELECT d.icd_code, COUNT(*) AS frequency
 FROM diagnoses_icd d
 JOIN admissions a ON d.hadm_id = a.hadm_id
 JOIN AgeFilteredPatients afp ON a.subject_id = afp.subject_id
 GROUP BY d.icd_code
),
RankedDiagnoses AS (
 SELECT df.icd_code, df.frequency, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY df.frequency DESC) AS rank
 FROM DiagnosisFrequency df
)
SELECT d.long_title
FROM RankedDiagnoses rd
JOIN d_icd_diagnoses d ON rd.icd_code = d.icd_code
WHERE rd.rank <= 4;

WITH arterial_procedures AS (
 SELECT DISTINCT subject_id, hadm_id, charttime
 FROM procedures_icd
 WHERE icd_code = 'ICD_CODE_FOR_ARTERIAL_CATHETERIZATION' 
 AND strftime('%Y', charttime) = '2100'
), 
lab_tests AS (
 SELECT le.subject_id, le.hadm_id, le.itemid, COUNT(*) AS test_count
 FROM labevents le
 JOIN arterial_procedures ap ON le.subject_id = ap.subject_id AND le.hadm_id = ap.hadm_id
 WHERE datetime(le.charttime, 'start of month') = datetime(ap.charttime, 'start of month')
 GROUP BY le.itemid
), 
ranked_tests AS (
 SELECT itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY test_count DESC) AS rank
 FROM lab_tests
)
SELECT d.label
FROM ranked_tests rt

)

WITH LastICUVisit AS (
 SELECT stay_id
 FROM icustays
 WHERE subject_id = 10004720
 ORDER BY intime DESC
 LIMIT 1
),
HeartRateMeasurements AS (
 SELECT valuenum, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY charttime) AS rn_first, 
 ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY charttime DESC) AS rn_last
 FROM chartevents
 WHERE subject_id = 10004720
 AND itemid = (SELECT itemid FROM d_items WHERE label = 'heart rate')
 AND stay_id = (SELECT stay_id FROM LastICUVisit)
)
SELECT CASE WHEN (SELECT valuenum FROM HeartRateMeasurements WHERE rn_last = 1) < 
 (SELECT valuenum FROM HeartRateMeasurements WHERE rn_first = 1)
 THEN 'True'
 ELSE 'False'
 END AS IsLastLessThanFirst;

WITH ProcedureEvents AS (
 SELECT pi.subject_id, pi.hadm_id, pi.charttime AS procedure_time

 JOIN d_icd_procedures dp ON pi.icd_code = dp.icd_code
 WHERE dp.long_title = 'central venous catheter placement with guidance'
 AND strftime('%Y', pi.charttime) = '2100'
),
DiagnosisEvents AS (

),

 FROM DiagnosisEvents de

),
RankedDiagnoses AS (

 FROM DiagnosisFrequency df
)

JOIN d_icd_diagnoses dd ON rd.icd_code = dd.icd_code
WHERE rd.rank <= 4;

 FROM diagnoses_icd AS D
 JOIN d_icd_diagnoses AS DD ON D.icd_code = DD.icd_code
 JOIN prescriptions AS P ON D.subject_id = P.subject_id AND D.hadm_id = P.hadm_id
 WHERE DD.long_title = 'acute and subacute hepatic failure without coma'
 AND datetime(D.charttime) >= datetime('2100-12-31 23:59:00', '-1 year')

 GROUP BY P.drug
 ORDER BY cnt DESC
 LIMIT 4
) AS top_treatments;

 FROM diagnoses_icd di

 WHERE dicd.long_title = 'Acute and subacute hepatic failure without coma'

),

 SELECT p.drug, COUNT(*) AS freq

 WHERE datetime(p.starttime) BETWEEN datetime(rd.charttime) AND datetime(rd.charttime, '+2 months')

)

ORDER BY freq DESC
LIMIT 4;

WITH recent_diagnoses AS (
 SELECT di.subject_id, di.hadm_id, di.charttime
 FROM diagnoses_icd di

 WHERE dicd.long_title = 'acute and subacute hepatic failure without coma'
 AND datetime(di.charttime) >= datetime('2100-12-31 23:59:00', '-1 year')
),
recent_admissions AS (
 SELECT ra.subject_id, ra.hadm_id, ra.admittime
 FROM admissions ra
 JOIN recent_diagnoses rd ON ra.hadm_id = rd.hadm_id
 WHERE julianday(ra.admittime) - julianday(rd.charttime) <= 60
),
frequent_treatments AS (
 SELECT p.drug, COUNT(*) as freq
 FROM prescriptions p
 JOIN recent_admissions ra ON p.hadm_id = ra.hadm_id

 GROUP BY p.drug
)
SELECT drug
FROM frequent_treatments
ORDER BY freq DESC
LIMIT 4;

WITH PneumothoraxDiagnoses AS (
 SELECT di.hadm_id
 FROM diagnoses_icd di
 JOIN d_icd_diagnoses dicd ON di.icd_code = dicd.icd_code
 WHERE dicd.long_title = 'Iatrogenic pneumothorax'
 AND strftime('%Y', di.charttime) = '2100'
),
SpecimenCounts AS (
 SELECT me.spec_type_desc, COUNT(*) AS freq
 FROM microbiologyevents me
 JOIN PneumothoraxDiagnoses pd ON me.hadm_id = pd.hadm_id
 WHERE strftime('%Y', me.charttime) = '2100'
 GROUP BY me.spec_type_desc
),
RankedSpecimens AS (

)

FROM RankedSpecimens
WHERE rank <= 5;

 WHERE subject_id = 10031757
 ORDER BY admittime ASC
 LIMIT 1
),
MonocyteMeasurements AS (
 SELECT labevents.valuenum, labevents.charttime
 FROM labevents
 JOIN FirstVisit ON labevents.hadm_id = FirstVisit.hadm_id
 JOIN d_labitems ON labevents.itemid = d_labitems.itemid
 WHERE d_labitems.label = 'monocytes'
 ORDER BY labevents.charttime
),
FirstAndLast AS (

 FROM MonocyteMeasurements
 ORDER BY charttime ASC
 LIMIT 1
 UNION ALL

 LIMIT 1
)

 SELECT AVG((JULIANDAY(outtime) - JULIANDAY(intime)) * 24.0) AS avg_duration
 FROM icustays
),
FilteredICUStays AS (
 SELECT (JULIANDAY(icustays.outtime) - JULIANDAY(icustays.intime)) * 24.0 AS duration
 FROM icustays
 JOIN admissions ON icustays.subject_id = admissions.subject_id AND icustays.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id
 WHERE admissions.age >= 60
)
SELECT AVG(duration) AS avg_longer_than_usual_duration
FROM FilteredICUStays
WHERE duration > (SELECT avg_duration FROM AvgICUStay);

WITH mortality_rate AS (
 SELECT 
 d.icd_code, 
 COUNT(CASE WHEN p.dod IS NOT NULL AND p.dod <= datetime(a.admittime, '+182 days') THEN 1 END) * 1.0 / COUNT(*) AS mortality_rate
 FROM 
 diagnoses_icd d
 JOIN 
 admissions a ON d.hadm_id = a.hadm_id
 JOIN 
 patients p ON a.subject_id = p.subject_id
 GROUP BY 
 d.icd_code
), ranked_diagnoses AS (
 SELECT 
 icd_code, 
 mortality_rate,
 DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY mortality_rate DESC) AS rank
 FROM 
 mortality_rate
)
SELECT 
 di.long_title
FROM 
 ranked_diagnoses rd
JOIN 
 d_icd_diagnoses di ON rd.icd_code = di.icd_code
WHERE 
 rd.rank <= 5;

WITH PatientAge AS (
 SELECT p.subject_id, a.hadm_id, 
 (strftime('%Y', a.admittime) - strftime('%Y', p.dob)) - 
 (strftime('%m-%d', a.admittime) < strftime('%m-%d', p.dob)) AS age
 FROM patients p
 JOIN admissions a ON p.subject_id = a.subject_id
),
DiagnosedPatients AS (
 SELECT DISTINCT pa.subject_id, pa.hadm_id, d.charttime
 FROM PatientAge pa
 JOIN diagnoses_icd d ON pa.subject_id = d.subject_id AND pa.hadm_id = d.hadm_id
 WHERE pa.age BETWEEN 40 AND 49
),
PrescriptionsWithin2Months AS (
 SELECT dp.subject_id, dp.hadm_id, pr.drug
 FROM DiagnosedPatients dp
 JOIN prescriptions pr ON dp.subject_id = pr.subject_id AND dp.hadm_id = pr.hadm_id
 WHERE datetime(pr.starttime) BETWEEN datetime(dp.charttime) AND datetime(dp.charttime, '+2 months')
)
SELECT drug
FROM PrescriptionsWithin2Months
GROUP BY drug
ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC
LIMIT 5;

WITH procedure_codes AS (
 SELECT icd_code
 FROM d_icd_procedures
 WHERE long_title = 'other endoscopy of small intestine'
),
initial_diagnoses AS (
 SELECT DISTINCT subject_id, charttime AS diagnosis_time
 FROM procedures_icd
 WHERE icd_code IN (SELECT icd_code FROM procedure_codes)
 AND charttime >= '2100-01-01'
),
follow_up_procedures AS (
 SELECT DISTINCT subject_id
 FROM procedures_icd
 WHERE icd_code IN (SELECT icd_code FROM procedure_codes)
 AND charttime >= '2100-01-01'
)
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT id.subject_id) AS patient_count
FROM initial_diagnoses id
JOIN follow_up_procedures fp ON id.subject_id = fp.subject_id
WHERE fp.charttime BETWEEN id.diagnosis_time AND DATETIME(id.diagnosis_time, '+61 days');

WITH MedicationFrequency AS (
 SELECT 
 P.drug, 
 COUNT(*) AS frequency
 FROM 
 diagnoses_icd AS D
 JOIN 
 prescriptions AS P ON D.subject_id = P.subject_id AND D.hadm_id = P.hadm_id
 WHERE 
 datetime(D.charttime, 'start of month') = datetime(P.starttime, 'start of month')
 GROUP BY 
 P.drug
), RankedMedications AS (
 SELECT 
 drug, 
 DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY frequency DESC) AS rank
 FROM 
 MedicationFrequency
)
SELECT 
 drug
FROM 
 RankedMedications
WHERE 
 rank <= 3;

WITH anion_gap_values AS (
 SELECT le.valuenum
 FROM admissions AS a
 JOIN labevents AS le ON a.subject_id = le.subject_id AND a.hadm_id = le.hadm_id
 JOIN d_labitems AS dli ON le.itemid = dli.itemid
 WHERE dli.label = 'anion gap'
 AND a.age = (
 SELECT age
 FROM admissions
 WHERE subject_id = (SELECT subject_id FROM admissions ORDER BY admittime ASC LIMIT 1)
 ORDER BY admittime ASC
 LIMIT 1
 )
),
ranked_values AS (
 SELECT valuenum, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY valuenum) AS rank
 FROM anion_gap_values
)
SELECT 100.0 * (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM ranked_values WHERE valuenum < 13.0) / (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM ranked_values) AS percentile;

SELECT DISTINCT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title AS diagnosis, d_icd_procedures.long_title AS procedure, d_labitems.label AS lab_test, prescriptions.drug AS drug
FROM patients
JOIN admissions ON patients.subject_id = admissions.subject_id
JOIN diagnoses_icd ON admissions.hadm_id = diagnoses_icd.hadm_id
LEFT JOIN d_icd_diagnoses ON diagnoses_icd.icd_code = d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code
LEFT JOIN procedures_icd ON admissions.hadm_id = procedures_icd.hadm_id
LEFT JOIN d_icd_procedures ON procedures_icd.icd_code = d_icd_procedures.icd_code
LEFT JOIN labevents ON admissions.hadm_id = labevents.hadm_id
LEFT JOIN d_labitems ON labevents.itemid = d_labitems.itemid
LEFT JOIN prescriptions ON admissions.hadm_id = prescriptions.hadm_id
WHERE patients.dod IS NOT NULL
AND DATE(patients.dod) <= DATE(diagnoses_icd.charttime, '+3 months')
AND DATE(patients.dod) >= DATE(diagnoses_icd.charttime);

SELECT AVG((julianday(COALESCE(patients.dod, '2100-12-31')) - julianday(patients.dob)) / 365.25) AS average_lifespan_years
FROM patients
JOIN diagnoses_icd ON patients.subject_id = diagnoses_icd.subject_id
WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code IN ('<specific_chronic_disease_icd_codes>')
AND patients.dod IS NOT NULL;
c4f0cff6d99c3b69c529315b:
SELECT A.hadm_id, A.admission_type, (JULIANDAY(A.dischtime) - JULIANDAY(A.admittime)) AS length_of_stay, SUM(C.cost) AS total_cost 
FROM admissions AS A 
JOIN procedures_icd AS P ON A.hadm_id = P.hadm_id 
JOIN cost AS C ON P.row_id = C.event_id AND C.event_type = 'procedures_icd' 
GROUP BY A.hadm_id, A.admission_type, length_of_stay;

SELECT p.subject_id, p.gender, a.age, d.icd_code AS diagnosis, pr.icd_code AS procedure, l.itemid AS lab_test, l.valuenum AS lab_value, pres.drug 
FROM patients p 
JOIN admissions a ON p.subject_id = a.subject_id 
JOIN diagnoses_icd d ON a.hadm_id = d.hadm_id 
JOIN procedures_icd pr ON a.hadm_id = pr.hadm_id 
JOIN labevents l ON a.hadm_id = l.hadm_id 
JOIN prescriptions pres ON a.hadm_id = pres.hadm_id 
WHERE a.dischtime IS NOT NULL 
GROUP BY p.gender, a.age, d.icd_code, pr.icd_code, l.itemid, pres.drug 
ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC;

WITH primary_department AS (
 SELECT first_careunit
 FROM icustays
 WHERE subject_id = 10008454
 LIMIT 1
),

lab_tests AS (
 SELECT DISTINCT d_labitems.label AS test_name
 FROM labevents
 JOIN d_labitems ON labevents.itemid = d_labitems.itemid
 JOIN transfers ON labevents.hadm_id = transfers.hadm_id
 WHERE labevents.subject_id = 10008454
 AND transfers.careunit NOT IN (SELECT first_careunit FROM primary_department)
),

micro_tests AS (
 SELECT DISTINCT microbiologyevents.test_name
 FROM microbiologyevents
 JOIN transfers ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = transfers.hadm_id
 WHERE microbiologyevents.subject_id = 10008454
 AND transfers.careunit NOT IN (SELECT first_careunit FROM primary_department)
)

SELECT test_name FROM lab_tests
UNION
SELECT test_name FROM micro_tests;
